title: Fancy Product Designer 3.8.41 - WooCommerceWordPress Plugin
description: Visit us on: https://www.nulledforums.org Compose your own interface by using various layouts. Use Fancy Product Designer WordPress Plugin to create and sell practically any kind of product you can think of. Fancy Product Designer WordPress Plugin fully responsive and easy to every device without losing functionality. You are easily able to translate the plugin into any language. Assign a set price for every additional layer as well as by layer type or for different product views Fancy Product Designer WordPress Plugin Features Set up your own font library using custom, system or Google fonts Customers can create curved, outlined or even patterned text and apply standard modification options like bold, italic, underline, alignment etc. Images and graphics can be transformed with various options like changing position, size, rotation and opacity Images can be applied with a grayscale or two different sepia filters
